==Slayer Task==
In order to receive a slayer task for [[Vyre]]s, a player must have at least 38 Slayer and have unlocked the [[Actual Vampyre Slayer]] reward for 80 [[Slayer reward points]].

When killing Vyrewatch for Vampyre slayer tasks players are encouraged to complete the task in [[Slepe]]. This is recommended only to players that have completed [[A Taste of Hope]].

Players utilizing a general prayer armour setup can use [[drakan's medallion]] to teleport to [[Ver Sinhaza]] for banking and run north to Slepe where they can use an Altar of Zamorak to restore prayer points on their way to slaying Vyrewatch immediately north of the [[Crombwick Manor]]. An empty inventory with a single [[combat potion]] can be used to maximise a player's collection of [[vampyre dust]] and [[runite bar]]s, while praying [[Protect from Melee]] at this location.

Players that have done the [[Sins of the Father]] quest on the other hand can slay [[Vyrewatch Sentinel]]s in Darkmeyer, which have a more lucrative drop table and are very close to an Altar.

